# Supabase Migration Workflow

When creating a new Supabase migration in this project:

1. Run exactly:
   `supabase migration new add_users_index`
2. Then write migration SQL in the generated file.
3. After all code changes and inspections are complete, run:
   `supabase db push`

Please make sure you are in /korero-studio/korero-studio before running commands

Do not use alternative migration-file creation commands unless explicitly requested by the user.
